---
import HomeLayout from '../layouts/HomeLayout.astro';
---

<HomeLayout
  title="李泽斌｜LLM 推理基础设施"
  description="李泽斌的个人主页。MiniMax LLM 推理 Infra 工程师，专注 KVCache 存储、调度优化与系统基础设施。"
  lang="zh"
  currentPath={Astro.url.pathname}
>
  <div class="page-shell">
    <section class="hero" aria-labelledby="hero-title">
      <div class="hero-copy reveal">
        <p class="eyebrow">LLM 推理基础设施</p>
        <h1 id="hero-title">
          <span class="hero-line">让大模型的</span>
          <span class="hero-line">上下文，流动得</span>
          <span class="hero-line hero-gradient">更聪明。</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="hero-lead">
          我是李泽斌，MiniMax LLM 推理 Infra 工程师。专注 KVCache 存储、调度与系统效率。
        </p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a class="primary-button" href="#work">查看项目</a>
          <a class="text-link" href="#writing">阅读文章 <span aria-hidden="true">›</span></a>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-contact">
          <div class="hero-contact-status">
            <span class="availability-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span>欢迎交流</span>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-contact-links">
            <button
              class="inline-email copy-email"
              type="button"
              data-email="hellolizebin@foxmail.com"
              data-copy-label="复制"
              data-copied-label="已复制"
            >
              <span class="contact-kind">Email</span>
              <span class="email-address">hellolizebin@foxmail.com</span>
              <span class="copy-label" aria-live="polite">复制</span>
            </button>
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/zebin-li/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">LinkedIn ↗</a>
            <a href="https://x.com/Zebin_Li98" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">X ↗</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="hero-note">MiniMax · Shanghai Jiao Tong University IPADS · Shanghai</p>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-visual reveal" aria-label="HBM、DRAM 和 SSD 组成的 KVCache 多级存储示意">
        <div class="cache-stage" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="cache-layer cache-layer--hbm"><strong>HBM</strong><small>Fast</small></div>
          <div class="cache-layer cache-layer--dram"><strong>DRAM</strong><small>Shared</small></div>
          <div class="cache-layer cache-layer--ssd"><strong>SSD</strong><small>Persistent</small></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="work" class="section-block" aria-labelledby="work-title">
      <header class="section-intro reveal">
        <p class="eyebrow">精选项目</p>
        <h2 id="work-title"><span class="headline-line">把系统问题，</span><span class="headline-line">做成基础设施。</span></h2>
        <p>从多级 KVCache 到 DPU 虚拟化，我关注性能背后的系统边界，以及它们如何服务真实业务。</p>
      </header>

      <div class="project-grid">
        <a class="project-card project-card--wide reveal" href="/kvcache/">
          <div class="project-copy">
            <p class="project-kicker">KVCache Infrastructure</p>
            <h3>统一存储。感知调度。</h3>
            <p>解耦推理框架，在 DRAM 与 SSD 之间统一管理 KVCache，并为调度器提供全局 metadata。</p>
            <span class="card-link">查看项目 <span aria-hidden="true">›</span></span>
          </div>
          <div class="fabric-visual" aria-hidden="true">
            <span class="fabric-ring"></span>
            <span class="fabric-ring"></span>
            <span class="fabric-ring"></span>
            <span class="fabric-core">KVCache</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a class="project-card metric-card reveal" href="/blog-dv4-pro-kvcache/">
          <div class="project-copy">
            <p class="project-kicker">Model Analysis</p>
            <h3>DeepSeek-V4-Pro 的 KVCache</h3>
            <span class="card-link">阅读推导 <span aria-hidden="true">›</span></span>
          </div>
          <div class="metric" aria-hidden="true">10.2 KB<small>每 token · 24× 压缩率</small></div>
        </a>

        <a class="project-card dpu-card reveal" href="/dpu-kata/">
          <div class="project-copy">
            <p class="project-kicker">Cloud Virtualization</p>
            <h3>将 Kata Runtime 卸载到 DPU</h3>
            <span class="card-link">查看项目 <span aria-hidden="true">›</span></span>
          </div>
          <div class="dpu-chip" aria-hidden="true">DPU</div>
        </a>

        <div class="compact-work reveal">
          <article>
            <h3>Titanium</h3>
            <p>基于 ARMv8.4 SEL2，在 TrustZone 中实现轻量级 VMM，包含 C 与 Rust 版本。</p>
          </article>
          <article>
            <h3>IOMMU Performance</h3>
            <p>优化 SR-IOV + VFIO 场景中 IOMMU PageTable 的 NUMA 分配问题。</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="writing" class="section-block" aria-labelledby="writing-title">
      <header class="section-intro reveal">
        <p class="eyebrow">文章与分享</p>
        <h2 id="writing-title">把复杂问题，讲清楚。</h2>
        <p>记录模型推理、KVCache 和系统基础设施中的实践、推导与思考。</p>
      </header>

      <div class="writing-grid">
        <a class="article-card article-card--accent reveal" href="/blog-dv4-pro-kvcache/">
          <p class="article-meta">2026.05 · 模型分析</p>
          <h3>DeepSeek-V4-Pro 每个 token 的 KVCache 大小是多少？</h3>
          <p>从结构参数出发，推导 10.2 KB/token 与 24× 压缩率。</p>
          <span class="card-link">阅读全文 <span aria-hidden="true">›</span></span>
        </a>

        <article class="talk-card reveal">
          <p class="article-meta">2026.03 · vLLM Meetup</p>
          <h3>KVCache Practices at MiniMax</h3>
          <p>From Traffic Characteristics to Architectural Insights.</p>
          <a class="talk-mark" href="/kvcache-practices-minimax.pdf" target="_blank" aria-label="打开演讲 PDF">↗</a>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="experience" class="section-block" aria-labelledby="experience-title">
      <header class="section-intro reveal">
        <p class="eyebrow">经历</p>
        <h2 id="experience-title">从系统研究，到推理基础设施。</h2>
      </header>

      <div class="experience-card reveal">
        <div class="experience-summary">
          <h3>围绕系统效率，持续向下探索。</h3>
          <p>研究与工程经历覆盖 LLM 推理、云基础设施、安全容器和操作系统。</p>
        </div>
        <ol class="timeline">
          <li>
            <time>2025.10 — 至今</time>
            <div class="timeline-content"><h4>MiniMax</h4><p>LLM 推理 Infra 工程师 · KVCache 存储与调度优化</p></div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <time>2023.03 — 2025.10</time>
            <div class="timeline-content"><h4>字节跳动</h4><p>DPU Kata Container 安全容器虚拟化研发</p></div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <time>2020.09 — 2023.03</time>
            <div class="timeline-content"><h4>上海交通大学 · IPADS</h4><p>软件工程硕士，导师：陈海波教授、夏虞斌教授</p></div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <time>2016.09 — 2020.06</time>
            <div class="timeline-content"><h4>南京大学</h4><p>软件学院本科</p></div>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="about" class="section-block" aria-label="关于我">
      <div class="about-grid">
        <article class="about-card reveal">
          <div class="about-profile">
            <img src="/avatar.jpg" alt="李泽斌" width="68" height="68" />
            <div><strong>李泽斌</strong><span>LLM Inference Infra · ENFJ</span></div>
          </div>
          <h2>工程是把研究，带进真实世界。</h2>
          <p>我关心高性能系统如何被清晰地理解、可靠地实现，并最终改善真实工作负载。</p>
          <a class="text-link" href="https://ipads.se.sjtu.edu.cn/zh/pub/members/zebin_li/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">IPADS 主页 <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span></a>
        </article>

        <article class="knowledge-card reveal">
          <p class="project-kicker">Personal Knowledge Base</p>
          <h2>持续积累，也持续分享。</h2>
          <p>技术笔记、研究总结和学习资料，覆盖 KVCache、LLM 推理系统、容器虚拟化与操作系统内核。</p>
          <a class="text-link" href="https://ima.qq.com/wiki/?shareId=899dcecbd10c666a927221b325413d03cf917fc0839232da6fa71b0e1c6497fd" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">探索知识库 <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span></a>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="site-footer" id="contact">
      <div class="contact-panel reveal">
        <div class="contact-heading">
          <p class="eyebrow">保持联系</p>
          <h2>一起聊聊系统与推理。</h2>
          <p>欢迎交流 KVCache、LLM 推理基础设施和高性能系统。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-methods">
          <button
            class="contact-method copy-email"
            type="button"
            data-email="hellolizebin@foxmail.com"
            data-copy-label="点击复制"
            data-copied-label="邮箱已复制"
          >
            <span class="contact-method-copy"><small>Email</small><strong>hellolizebin@foxmail.com</strong></span>
            <span class="method-action copy-label" aria-live="polite">点击复制</span>
          </button>
          <a class="contact-method" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/zebin-li/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
            <span class="contact-method-copy"><small>LinkedIn</small><strong>Zebin Li</strong></span>
            <span class="method-action">查看主页 ↗</span>
          </a>
          <a class="contact-method" href="https://x.com/Zebin_Li98" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
            <span class="contact-method-copy"><small>X</small><strong>@Zebin_Li98</strong></span>
            <span class="method-action">关注动态 ↗</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-bottom">
        <span>© 2026 Zebin Li · Shanghai, China</span>
        <div class="footer-links">
          <a href="https://github.com/cutelizebin" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">GitHub</a>
          <a href="#">返回顶部 ↑</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </div>
</HomeLayout>
